description:
Matthew Socey chats with film critic and scholar Jeff Marker about two female nautical films, The Thin Man film series and the films of Rutger Hauer.

PROGRAMMING NOTE: Film Soceyology will be going on vacation. The show will return on Aug. 16, 2019.
